Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.19,0:00:40.19,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是誰 對未來都著著一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.47,0:00:49.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝著明天大步邁進吧
