Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.71,0:00:58.08,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}總有一天會覺醒的 真實心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.35,0:01:04.19,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.39,0:01:14.43,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.67,0:01:20.44,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.48,0:01:23.53,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.58,0:01:28.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三號機接近目標中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.72,0:01:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.19,0:01:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四點鐘方向有敵影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.10,0:01:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捕捉目標集團 準備發射飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到 出力調至150%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄準範圍目標數28、29…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.44,0:02:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊那位 表情帥氣一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.07,0:02:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好   卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,0K了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.75,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第十一話  說不出口」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.19,0:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像剛才所示 兩人為了加強彼此的默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日夜都接受著嚴格的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事無所謂 快播下去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很吵耶 一直亂叫\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(那麼就採訪速水駕駛員)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊、來了來了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(速水是雙人座機駕駛員吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有拍到了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(是的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看在這 拍到我了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(那至今都跟芝村合作嗎）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.87,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水…\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(平常的休閒是？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙！\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(平常就是慢跑或讀書)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我的錯啦\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(最後請問一個問題)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村對你而言是怎樣的存在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得…是很好的搭檔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著採訪芝村 操縱工作很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 記得芝村後來是說…\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(沒什麼問題)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於芝村而言 速水是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很好的…工作上的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(非常感謝各位的協助)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還問怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.81,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道還有其他回答嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了 望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去哪裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說是工作上的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.76,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都到這個地步了 與其說頑固 倒不如是偏執呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.43,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.23,0:03:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水跟芝村最近的感覺不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會讓人忍不住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 趕快交往不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要等他們自然交往也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.51,0:04:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該有什麼辦法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學姊你說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.55,0:04:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上是來自尚敬高中5121部隊\N「突擊！話題之兩人」的專欄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.12,0:04:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了和平而戰鬥的兩人 希望各位為他們加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你很不滿呢 善行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都寫在臉上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.51,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那接下來要決定負責的工作\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(5121部隊聖誕派對)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負責購物的要男女各一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰負責比較好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得女生找芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後男生找速水就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有誰贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.89,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這麼問 剛剛決定的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不是工作上的搭檔嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是買東西的順序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前面沒買完 不准開後面的信封
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 你有意見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人在聖誕夜去買東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺就像在約會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師也有過美好的回憶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時我前一天就很緊張呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找朋友討論該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.78,0:05:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還煩惱要穿哪件衣服 這些過程都很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得沒有容身之處呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快把東西買完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標從通町路前往商店街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如預定前往A地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通知誘敵部隊 目標接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進入臨戰態勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以順利成功嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.98,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不都是春香無意間扯後腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣再失敗的話 我就生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想問一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來須請說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.99,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道 為什麼我是麋鹿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你想當聖誕老人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了 我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.84,0:06:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-聖誕快樂 現在是特惠活動喔\N-請參考看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(熱戀的二人之快速占卜)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 去買下一個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是聖誕老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經撒餌了 狀況進行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.79,0:07:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來須
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是你命中注定的伴侶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30分鐘之內被告白的話 你們的戀情將永誌不渝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸運物是木製的長椅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的眼中已經只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30分鐘之內告白 一定會成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸運物是噴水池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種亂七八糟的占卜好多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.99,0:07:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 害得年底的氣氛都怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.89,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是聖誕老人 任務結束 現在準備歸隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你笑他們的話 他們會很可憐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒在笑他們啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得趕快買完東西才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且大家都在等呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.53,0:08:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.17,0:08:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我其實很…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜…喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是很愛你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是衷心地愛你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼 我要走了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 美惠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得趕快去買東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水厚志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要丟下我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一階段失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 那個沒毅力的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.24,0:09:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事就是不簡單才有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你們了 快回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到 現在將前往交班地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊 接下來麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪位可以借我電車錢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠阪 跟她一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他不是真命天子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他分開之後的下一個才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-謝謝你了\N-謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位還記得嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.56,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尚敬高中5121部隊的那兩個人 在聖誕夜被我們抓到囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來感情很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的計劃是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看電影？喝下午茶？還是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜歡她哪個地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 她本人是聽不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是說你不好意思說出來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.45,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是工作上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.68,0:11:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是因為要買東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼接下來是女方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 請站在攝影機前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是這間店嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.85,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在這裏買外套跟長褲 而且配色要夠好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確定上面是這麼寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,配色？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年這一系列很受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需要幫您做介紹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是我要穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是朋友要我幫忙買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心不要被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是聖誕節的禮物嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那等到選好再通知我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖誕派對需要這些嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是遠阪 田邊嚴重受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在由這邊先行收容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊都是本店的新作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是這裏沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.07,0:12:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村 果然很奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.58,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派對不應該買這種高價飾品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚇死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點就被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過芝村應該也有所警覺了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 都已經走到這一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來只要任憑發展就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問要找什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,需要的話可以幫您拿出來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.07,0:13:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我們應該是搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.49,0:13:57.99,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a7}你一個不經意的舉止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.37,0:14:04.86,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}就讓我冰凍的心得以融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.27,0:14:12.14,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}回頭所露出令我心動的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.41,0:14:19.15,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}讓失去色彩的城市變得鮮艷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.89,0:14:25.88,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}我不知道未來會是如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:34.66,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}但我明天仍想仰望藍天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.16,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}好想要奔跑的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來是最後一個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.90,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}想這麼撲到你的懷裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.04,0:14:48.41,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,!Effect,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}你雙手接著我凝視著我 兩人一起乘風而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水厚志先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您已經預約好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.57,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫您把手提物品放在寄物櫃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.09,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您要點預約時所訂的聖誕特製晚餐A餐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.36,0:15:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.46,0:15:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得心怦怦跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.73,0:15:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過學姊知道的地方好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.47,0:15:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也好想在那種地方被告白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有訂到好位子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然 要看夜景絕對沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實只要吃飯不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們根本就是白費工夫嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運動型的不要說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這種是要順其自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.38,0:15:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 我所選的珠寶店可是讓小舞非常滿意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百元商店是我的意見喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.89,0:16:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說說誰曾經去那間店花大錢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可能是去讓別人花錢的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的百元商店…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得這趟購物之旅很奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒想到會有這麼一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.41,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.02,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道會是芝村先開口嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.42,0:16:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我至今都是一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.43,0:16:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使知道不會結束 從那天起我還是獨自走來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.53,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只希望能夠盡量多殺些幻獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問 那天是哪天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我將其當成是在繼承遺志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在對馬戰死的那個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道這只是在逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我想不到其他的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.62,0:17:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人背負一切作戰 然後在心中對自己妥協
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.16,0:17:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得這樣就行了 孤單一個人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被編到5121部隊時也這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.27,0:17:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次跟你搭乘雙人座機也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是忘不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘不了那個人對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.49,0:17:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,客人怎麼了嗎？客人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是白癡嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.07,0:18:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村舞 芝村舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請盡快到教職員室來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是本部的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.25,0:18:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你以雙人座機駕駛員的身份 前往缺人的8312部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換句話說 是轉調邀請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是邀請 不是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不願意的話可以拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何 決定權在於你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於還有一些時間 你就好好考慮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.24,0:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}昨天的聖誕夜各位怎麼過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.08,0:19:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}以下是黑川記者在街上的突擊採訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}各位好 我是黑川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,餐廳還有開嗎\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(馬上就來採訪這對情侶吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.79,0:19:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年好像開到29號\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(男朋友？不是啦)
